com.app.towerDefense.models

Interface CritterType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javafx.beans.Observable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdvancedCritter, BasicCritter

    public interface CritterType
extends javafx.beans.Observable
    This interface is defined as per factory pattern. In this interface we define the critter type and the basic methods associated with it which would be later used for creating different types of critters.
    Author:
    Amritansh Mishra
